{"type": "article", "id": 18303, "title": "地毯椅", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-01T07:20:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 23, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606071135382F6wXcr03zOQBZ7H.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一些可拼接的方形地毯，由一块带颜色的和三块白色的组成一组。将彩色地毯旁边的一块折叠在彩色的下面，两块白色的地毯立起来成为靠背，就是一张贴在地面上的简易座椅，还可以随意晃动。设计者是一位刚毕业的荷兰设计师 Sam Linders ，这张可改变功能的地毯也更适合年轻人。<a href=\"http://www.samlinders.com/portfolio/interior/wobble-up/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607113536gpwOayKcYTzJMXxD.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.55333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071135365SpNVxMf926bkDeO.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.59333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607113537tuJIyWkj0MDNBvGc.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607113537JC7nKvY9LGQP6rqe.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.46666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607113538ClERn6WzYgKM4VSx.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.65166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}